" create a go doc comment based on the word under the cursor
function! s:create_go_doc_comment()
  norm "zyiw
  execute ":put! z"
  execute ":norm I// \<Esc>$"
endfunction
au FileType go nmap <silent> <Leader>go :<C-u>call <SID>create_go_doc_comment()<CR>

